[Given the numerous possibilities with the limited clinical information
available, it would be of little help to speculate on the etiology of this
outbreak. With the information above, the GIDEON program identified over 20
infectious agents able to produce a fatal outcome compatible with these
symptoms that are known to have occurred in Brazil. We await further
information. - Man. Ed. DS
